cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Bibliothecarius Modernus: Latin Patristic Translations"
message: "If you use or reference these translations, please cite as below."
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Wolfslayer
    given-names: Ryan
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8914-9706"
    affiliation: Bibliothecarius Modernus
repository-code: "https://github.com/bibliothecarius-modernus/bibliothecarius-modernus.github.io"
url: "https://bibliothecarius-modernus.github.io"
abstract: >-
  AI-assisted translations of Latin Patristic texts from sources including
  Patrologia Latina. Translations produced using Claude (Anthropic) with
  human direction, selection, and editorial review. Provides side-by-side
  Latin and English text for verification. Covers works from the Apostolic
  Fathers through medieval theologians, many lacking prior English translations.
keywords:
  - patristics
  - Latin
  - translation
  - church fathers
  - medieval theology
  - Patrologia Latina
  - AI-assisted translation
